    .description-body
      I've partnered with Jules from Expedition Colombia in Medellín to chart a unique route for this expedition. We’ll start high in the mountains outside of Medellín and end in the Colombian lowlands; 5 days, 4 nights, and a lot of water. This is a 10 day trip, but the focus is undoubtedly the rafting adventure.
      <br>
      <br>
      You will be a member on a purposeful expedition, not a guest on a tour. We’ll need 8 seriously adventurous travelers to get this journey off the ground. Bonus points to those who can speak spanish! We guarantee you'll end up with a few crazy stories to tell when the journey is over, and more than likely a few incredible friends.

